__More information__

- the module is a plain text JavaScript file with `.js` extension
- the framework loads all modules
- all modules are stored in `your-app/modules/` directory
- `exports.install` method is executed automatically and once
- you can create unlimited number of modules
- the module can be injected from the URL address, [example](https://github.com/totaljs/examples/tree/master/framework-install-module).
- the module can communicate with other modules or controllers
- [Download modules](https://my.totaljs.com)

